{"id": "jos024", "name": "Call_Diego_701_06_25", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Call Starts]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Hello, brother Fang? Gimme a sec, I'm cleaning a glass...\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Hi, JOE.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... Diego!? Why did you call me yourself?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "The next job is very crucial. So I decided to inform you directly.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "Arf... Arf!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Woah! Zark...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Playing with the dog?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "One moment please... get down you dumb dog... can't you see that I'm working?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Apologies, I'm back. So what's this crucial job?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Three days later, secret code: \"Devil's puppet\". Hunter will be on-site to supervise everything. You get it, right?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Puppet?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Yes.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... A human, isn't it? Another kidnapping?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "F***! Wise up! Now I have to spend money to erase this phone call from the records.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Hunter told me that you helped out a few years ago. You know what to do then.\nThese types of buyers are very rare, but the payment is usually significant. Both you and I can make a fortune out of this deal.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Hmm...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "What's wrong?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Nothing.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "... JOE, do you know what I see when I look at you?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... Huh?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "The answer is myself. Your eyes show my reflection. Maybe you think you've kept it well-hidden, but I'm always there. You and I are the same. What you see, what you hear, what you think, I know it like the back of my hand.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "So, you just need to do one thing... tell me, whatever is on your mind. Tell me clearly, word by word.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "I...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "I'm listening.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Recently... I've been thinking about this a lot. I still feel like this is not good. Pops' ideals exist for their reasons. I don't understand them back then, still don't really understand them now, but...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Your conclusion?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "I don't want to break the law anymore! In the future, JOEZ Cafe will return to what it used to be. I will only offer services to legal transactions and maintain the current balance... even though you guys are already by far the largest gang now.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Hello?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "... I've been expecting you to say that, JOE.\nWe've been partners for a long time now. To be honest, I already noticed that your mind was struggling.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Is that so...?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "However, I've already accepted this deal. Canceling it now will do great harm to my credibility. Take this as a final request. Help me out on this case, and we'll talk about the details after its done. Deal?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... Alright.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Boy, I've been in the gang business since I was 15. It's been decades. Yet you're the only person in my career so far that feels \"alive\" to me. I won't let you suffer.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... Thank you!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "No need for that. Go play with your dog.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Call Ends]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話開始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "もしもし？Fang兄貴？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "おう、JOEか？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……Diegoさん！？なんでわざわざ電話なんか？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "次の仕事はかなり重要な仕事だ。\n私から直接話そう。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "ワン…ワン！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "うお！？Zark……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "犬とじゃれてるのか？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "ちょっと待って……あっち行けって。バカ犬……\n俺今忙しいんだって。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "悪い悪い。\nで、仕事って？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "3日後、合言葉は「悪魔の傀儡」だ。\nHunterも監視しに行く。分かったな？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "「傀儡」？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "そうだ。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……人間？また誘拐か？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "おい、もう少し頭を使え！バカが！\n今、お前が余計な発言をしたせいで、記録が残っちまった。\n余計な金を使わなきゃなんねぇだろうが。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "前回も手伝ったことがあるそうだな。\nこの手の取引は、買い手が多くない。\nだが、1回の報酬がデカい。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "あぁ……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "どうした？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "いや、なんでも。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……JOE、私がお前の前に立っている時、何が見えているか知ってるか？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……え？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "答えは私自身だ。\nお前の瞳の中に私の影を見ている。\nお前はうまく隠しているつもりかもしれないが、私はお前の瞳の中にいる。\nお前は私と一緒だ。\nお前の見たもの、聞いたもの、考えていること、全て把握している。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "つまり、お前のすべきことは一つだ……\n私に言いたいことを、全て話せ。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "俺は……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "あぁ。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "最近……ずっと考えてて、思ったんだ。\nやっぱり、こんなのダメだって。\nいつでも、親父の考えは正しかった。\n俺は、ガキで分かんないこともいっぱいあったけど……でも……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "お前の結論はなんだ。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "俺は、もうやりたくない！\nこれから、JOEZ Cafeは昔みたいに、合法取引にだけ手を貸す。\nそれで、今の勢力の現状を保つ……\n今は、あんたらが、一大勢力だけど……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "もしもし？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……そう言うと思っていた。\nJOE、共に仕事をするうちに、お前の葛藤などとうに見抜いていた。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "え……？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "だが、この取引は、すでに引き受けてしまった。\n今からノーと言えば、我々の看板に傷がつく。\nこうしよう。これが最後だ。\nこれを最後の取引として、今後どのように事を片付けるかは、また話し合おう。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……分かった。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "JOE、私は15歳でこの世界に足を踏み入れて、もう数十年になる。\nこの数十年で「人間」を感じたのはお前だけだ。\nお前を苦しませたりなどしない。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……ありがとう……！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "あぁ、犬と遊んでやれ。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話終了]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話開始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "喂，Fang 哥？等等，我在洗杯子……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "嗨，JOE。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……Diego！？怎麼親自打電話來？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "下一份工作很重要，所以我直接找你說。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "汪……汪！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哇！Zark……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "在和狗玩啊？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "等我一下……下去啦，智障狗……沒看到我在忙啊？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "抱歉抱歉，我回來了。你說有重要的工作是？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "三天後，暗語是「惡魔傀儡」，Hunter 也會在場監督。你懂吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "「傀儡」？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "嗯。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……是人吧？又是綁架嗎？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "○的！放聰明點！你讓我得多花一筆錢處理這通電話了。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Hunter 和我說過，幾年前你有幫過一次忙，那就好辦了。\n這種買家不多，但報酬非常驚人，你我都能大賺一筆。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "沒事。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……JOE，你知道當我面對著你時，會看見什麼嗎？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……嗯？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "答案是我自己，你眼裡映出的我的倒影。\n也許你以為藏得很好，但我就在那裡。你跟我是一樣的，你的所見所聞、所有想法，我都瞭若指掌。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "所以，你只需要做一件事……想和我說的話，把它明確地說出來。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "我在聽。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "這陣子……我想了很多，覺得這樣還是不好。老爹的想法有他的道理，很多時候我都搞不懂，但是……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "你的結論？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我不想再犯法了！以後的 JOEZ Cafe 會和以前一樣，只提供合法的交易，維持現在的勢力狀況……雖然你們已經是第一大幫了。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "喂？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……我猜到你會這麼說了，JOE。\n我們合作這麼久，其實我早就看出來你心裡很掙扎。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "是嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "但是這筆生意我已經接了，現在反悔有損我商譽。你就當幫我最後一筆，做完後我們再討論怎麼收，好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……好吧。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "小子，我十五歲就開始在黑道混了，好幾十年了，但我只在你身上，才感受到了「活人」的味道。我不會讓你難受的。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……謝謝你！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "沒事，去陪狗吧。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話結束]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[통화 시작]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "여보세요? Fang 형? 잠깐만, 지금 컵 좀 씻고……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "여어, JOE.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……Diego!? 웬일로 직접 전화를?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "매우 중요한 일거리가 잡혔어.\n그래서 내가 직접 전화로 전달하려 한다.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "왈!……왈!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "으앗! Zark……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "지금...개랑 놀고 있는 건가...?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "잠깐만…… 좀 내려 가라고 이 똥개 자식아!.... 지금 바쁜 거 안보여?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "미안 미안~ 지금 왔어. 방금 중요한 일거리라고 했지?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "3일 후, 암호는 「악마의 꼭두각시」. Hunter도 현장에 감독관으로 나갈 예정이다. 알아들었나?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "「꼭두각시」？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "그래.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……사람...인가? 또 납치한 거야?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "X신 같은 놈! 제발 눈 좀 뜨라고! \n게다기 지금 이 통화 기록을 지우려면 또 돈을 써야 한단 말이다!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Hunter가 나한테 말했지. 몇 년 전 너도 그 일을 해봤었다고 말이야. 그럼 어려울 거 없잖아. 이런 일거리는 자주 들어오지 않는다고. 게다가 보상은 또 엄청나지. 너 와 나, 크게 한몫 쥘 수 있는 기회다.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "아...…\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "왜 그러지?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "아니, 아무것도.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……JOE. 내가 널 볼 때 말이야,\n내가 무엇을 보는지 아나?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……응?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "바로 내 자신, 네 눈동자에 비치는 내 모습이다. 네가 아무리 무엇을 숨기려고 해도, 난 바로 그곳에 있지. 네가 무엇을 보든, 무엇을 듣든, 무엇을 생각하든, 모두 알 수 있지.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "즉 네가 할 일은 단 하나.... 내게 말하고 싶은 것이 있다면 모두 확실하게 말하는 것이 좋을 거야.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "난……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "듣고 있다.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "최근에…… 계속 생각이 들었어. 아무리 생각해도 이건 아닌 것 같다고. 영감은 자신만의 신념대로 일을 처리했었지. 그땐 나도 이해하지 못했어. 하지만……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "그래서 결론은?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "난... 범죄에는 가담하고 싶지 않아! 앞으로도 JOEZ Cafe에선 예전처럼 합법적인 거래만 제공하고 현재 세력의 균형을 유지하는...... 물론 지금 이미 너희들의 세력이 가장 커버렸지만.....\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "여보세요?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……나도 네가 이렇게 말할 줄 알고 있었다, JOE. 난 오랜시간 너와 함께 해왔다. 네가 갈등하고 있다는 것쯤은 진작에 알아차릴 수 있었다.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "그래……？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "하지만 이번 일거리는 이미 수락을 한 상태야. 지금와서 못하겠다고 한다면 우리도 꽤 큰 타격을 입게 돼. 그러니 마지막으로 나를 도와주도록 해. 우선 이 거래를 끝내고 다시 그 이야기를 해보자고. 어떤가?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……알았어.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "JOE. 난 15살부터 이 더러운 바닥에서 수십 년간 쉬지 않고 굴러왔다. 하지만 어느 순간  네 곁에 있을 때 비로소 내가 「인간」답게 변하고 있다고 느껴지더군. 절대 널 곤란하게 만들지 않을 테니 걱정하지 마라.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……그렇게 말해줘서 정말 고마워....!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "고마워할 필요 없다. 어서 그 개나 잘 돌보라고.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[통화 종료]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話開始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "喂，Fang 哥？等等，我在洗杯子……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "嗨，JOE。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……Diego！？怎麼親自打電話來？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "下一份工作很重要，所以我直接找你說。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "汪……汪！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哇！Zark……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "在和狗玩啊？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "等我一下……下去啦，智障狗……沒看到我在忙啊？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "抱歉抱歉，我回來了。你說有重要的工作是？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "三天後，暗語是「惡魔傀儡」，Hunter 也會在場監督。你懂吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "「傀儡」？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "嗯。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……是人吧？又是綁架嗎？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "○的！放聰明點！你讓我得多花一筆錢處理這通電話了。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Hunter 和我說過，幾年前你有幫過一次忙，那就好辦了。\n這種買家不多，但報酬非常驚人，你我都能大賺一筆。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "沒事。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……JOE，你知道當我面對著你時，會看見什麼嗎？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……嗯？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "答案是我自己，你眼裡映出的我的倒影。\n也許你以為藏得很好，但我就在那裡。你跟我是一樣的，你的所見所聞、所有想法，我都瞭若指掌。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "所以，你只需要做一件事……想和我說的話，把它明確地說出來。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "我在聽。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "這陣子……我想了很多，覺得這樣還是不好。老爹的想法有他的道理，很多時候我都搞不懂，但是……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "你的結論？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我不想再犯法了！以後的 JOEZ Cafe 會和以前一樣，只提供合法的交易，維持現在的勢力狀況……雖然你們已經是第一大幫了。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "喂？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……我猜到你會這麼說了，JOE。\n我們合作這麼久，其實我早就看出來你心裡很掙扎。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "是嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "但是這筆生意我已經接了，現在反悔有損我商譽。你就當幫我最後一筆，做完後我們再討論怎麼收，好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……好吧。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "小子，我十五歲就開始在黑道混了，好幾十年了，但我只在你身上，才感受到了「活人」的味道。我不會讓你難受的。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……謝謝你！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "沒事，去陪狗吧。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話結束]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通话开始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "喂，Fang 哥？等等，我在洗杯子……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "嗨，JOE。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……Diego！ ？怎么亲自打电话来？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "下一份工作很重要，所以我直接找你说。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "汪……汪！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哇！ Zark……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "在和狗玩啊？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "等我一下……下去啦，智障狗……没看到我在忙啊？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "抱歉抱